| Label               = [[Atlantic Records|Atlantic]], [[Candid Records|Candid]], [[Columbia Records|Columbia]], [[Debut Records|Debut]], [[Impulse! Records|Impulse!]], [[Mercury Records|Mercury]], [[United Artists Records|United Artists]]
