This chart showing the runes shared by the ''Angerthas Daeron'' and ''Angerthas Moria'' is presented in Appendix E of ''[[The Return of the King (book)|The Return of the King]]''. Some of the ''cirth'' had different values for the [[Elvish languages (Middle-earth)|Elvish]] and [[Khuzdul|Dwarvish]] languages and some were used in only one system or the other.  Where two values are given connected with a hyphen, the first is that of the older Angerthas, the second that of the dwarvish Angerthas Moria. Letters with asterisk are dwarvish only, values in brackets elvish only.

