==Current projects==
Several important projects include [[Interstate 105 (California)|Interstate 105]], the reconstruction of the [[California State Route 91|SR 91]]/[[California State Route 60|SR 60]]/[[Interstate 215 (California)|I-215]] interchange, the [[San Francisco – Oakland Bay Bridge]] (East Span), and the [[Devil's Slide (California)|Devil's Slide]] tunnel on Highway 1 in San Mateo County scheduled to be completed in 2011.

