&lt;!--Note to editors: This page has been replaced as per the discussion page. Please do not take offense and feel free to add to the page. Please remember though that this page is meant to concentrate on Steve Rogers as Captain America other additions should be made at the appropriate pages currently listed under [[Captain America (disambiguation)]]. Thank you. ~~~~--&gt;

