A '''[[cyclops]]''' is a one-eyed monster in Greek mythology.

'''Cyclops''' or '''The Cyclops''' may also refer to:
{{TOCright}}
==Arts and entertainment==
===Literature===
* [[Cyclops (play)|''Cyclops'' (play)]], a play by Euripides
