* [[Cyclops (comics)]], a superhero in the Marvel Comics universe
* ''Cyclops'', a comic poem by [[Philoxenus of Cythera]]
* &quot;The Cyclops&quot;, an episode of James Joyce's novel ''[[Ulysses (novel)#Episode 12, Cyclops|Ulysses]]''
